PTorrent — What's New
======================

Version 2.0 (2026-05-30)
--------------------------

PTorrent file format defined. The .ptorrent JSON descriptor is now the
canonical distribution unit for corpus seeding jobs — analogous to a
.torrent file, but for knowledge corpora rather than arbitrary data.

  * Two delivery paths: adb inbox/ push and tap-to-open via intent filters
  * Corpus detail page with live URL-level status tracking
  * Transmission-style control bar: Resume / Pause / Clear / Add
  * Physics (~130 URLs) and Mathematics (~130 URLs) corpora shipped
  * seed_runner.py now exports run_one() for single-PTorrent seeding
  * Chaquopy 15.0.1 bridge, Python 3.12 embedded

Version 1.0 (2026-05-26)
--------------------------

Initial release. Five corpora seeded in parallel across Android devices.
BitTorrent-inspired architecture without tracker, gradient server, or
central coordinator. Corpus traversal runs entirely on-device.
